      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 648,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "Slack Multilingual Assistant (Gemini 2.5 Flash)\n\nüîß Three translation modes unified in one workflow:\n1Ô∏è‚É£ /trans ‚Äî Public bilingual announcements  \n‚ÄÉ‚ÄÉFormat: „Äêfrom @user„Äë Original ---------- Translation  \n2Ô∏è‚É£ @trans ‚Äî Mention trigger for thread translation (translation only)  \n3Ô∏è‚É£ üáØüáµ / üá∫üá∏ Reaction ‚Äî Private on-demand translation  \n\nüí° All modes share the same Google Gemini 2.5 Flash core for automatic JA‚áÑEN detection."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
