      "parameters": {
        "color": 3,
        "width": 480,
        "height": 272,
        "content": "üö® Common Errors & Fixes\n\n‚ùå invalid_auth  \n‚ÄÉ‚Üí Using an old token or bot not invited to channel  \n‚ÄÉ‚ÄÉFix: Reinstall app / use latest xoxb token / `/invite @TransBot`\n\n‚ùå missing_scope  \n‚ÄÉ‚Üí A required scope is missing  \n‚ÄÉ‚ÄÉFix: Add scope in OAuth & Permissions ‚Üí Save ‚Üí Reinstall\n\n‚ùå no message found  \n‚ÄÉ‚Üí Reaction event can‚Äôt fetch original text  \n‚ÄÉ‚ÄÉFix: Add `groups:history` scope for private channels"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
